<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[البِرْجِيس]</span>: نجم <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
